org.apache.flink.streaming.api.datastream

Class WindowDataStream<OUT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.streaming.api.datastream.BatchedDataStream<OUT>
      • org.apache.flink.streaming.api.datastream.WindowDataStream<OUT>
  • Type Parameters:
    OUT - The output type of the WindowDataStream

    public class WindowDataStream<OUT>
extends BatchedDataStream<OUT>
    A WindowDataStream represents a data stream whose elements are batched together in a sliding window. operations like BatchedDataStream.reduce(ReduceFunction) or BatchedDataStream.reduceGroup(GroupReduceFunction) are applied for each window and the window is slid afterwards.
